These two stations have data going back to 1892 and 1899 respectively.
As we know NASA has been busy over the last years adjusting and homogenizing data from stations around the world, again and again. Data which once stood for years, suddenly got altered ‚Äì in many cases very substantially. Greece here is another example.
What follows are side-by-side plots of the two stations: V4 unadjusted and V4 adjusted:

The two GHCN V4 unadjusted mean annual temperature data plots of the respective stations clearly show a cooling trend.
So no wonder we are seeing ‚Äúrare‚Äù snow and cold in April.
NASA‚Äôs claimed warming is statistically fabricated
But NASA altered the data for the two Greek stations and named the two new data sets ‚ÄúV4 adjusted‚Äù. Clearly the adjustments magically produce the warming they like to scream about.
The warming didn‚Äôt occur because the air warmed up, but rather because NASA changed the data. The warming is a fake.
Though lots of people, media and politicians are listening and believing it, the weather isn‚Äôt. Snow and cold continue to make their appearance, Greece and other places are showing.


